0of%20my%20children's%20events%20I%20can%20attend.%20When%20I%20first%20started%20my%20practice%2C%20I%20didn't%20block%20my%20schedule%20for%20certain%20school%20events.%20After%20my%20oldest%20child%20shared%20with%20me%20that%20he%20missed%20having%20me%20at%20these%20events%2C%20I%20started%20proactively%20blocking%20out%20time%20for%20my%20children%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20requesting%20classroom%20activities%20from%20teachers%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20school%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20I%20always%20take%20off%20Halloween%20for%20classroom%20parties%20and%20second-semester%20field%20trips.%20In%20the%20office%2C%20We've%20established%20color%20codes%20on%20my%20calendar%20so%20they're%20aware%20when%20a%20calendar%20event%20is%20non-negotiable%20and%20dedicated%20to%20my%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20my%20kids%20get%20older%2C%20I%20make%20those%20decisions%20with%20input%20from%20my%20kids%20about%20what%20events%20are%20most%20meaningful%20to%20them.%20I%20cancel%20work%20for%20one%20on-campus%20activity%20per%20kid%20a%20year.%20On%20those%20days%2C%20we%20go%20all%20out.%20It%20isn't%20just%20a%20stop%20by%20the%20school%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20we%20dress%20up%20and%20plan%20our%20activities%20weeks%20in%20advance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20excitement%2C%20and%20mine%20as%20well%2C%20have%20shown%20me%20it%20isn't%20the%20number%20of%20events%20you're%20at%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20but%20your%20presence%20at%20the%20ones%20you%20can%20come%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20sacrificed%20at%20work%20too.%20I%20moved%20to%20running%20my%20practice%20versus%20the%20world%20of%20medical%20academia.%20In%20opening%20my%20practice%2C%20I%20had%20to%20make%20the%20tough%20decision%20to%20stop%20working%20with%20trainees.%20Though%20I%20love%20teaching%2C%20it%20slows%20down%20cases%20and%20I%20had%20to%20prioritize%20my%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2F