0FBI%20will%20not%20tolerate%20acts%20of%20violence%20or%20other%20efforts%20to%20retaliate%20against%20those%20residing%20in%20the%20US%20for%20exercising%20their%20constitutionally%20protected%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20FBI%20director%20Christopher%20Wray%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20is%20accused%20of%20recruiting%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20in%20May%202023%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20Mr%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20Prague%20in%20June%20that%20year%2C%20after%20travelling%20from%20India%2C%20and%20was%20subsequently%20extradited%20to%20the%20US%2C%20where%20he%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20and%20Mr%20Gupta%20allegedly%20contracted%20an%20individual%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20killing%20for%20%24100%2C000.%20The%20FBI%20later%20discovered%20that%20the%20hired%20assassin%20was%20an%20informant%20for%20the%20agency%20who%20was%20working%20undercover.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736946480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fl8063v1o_gurpatwant-singh-pannun-twitter_625x300_12_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurpatwant-singh-pannun-assassination-plot-vikash-yadav-indian-panel-recommends-action-against-ex-spy-cc1-in-us-murder-plot-case-7479393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20recommended%20that%20legal%20action%20be%20taken%20against%20a%20former%20Indian%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20identified%20as%20'CC1'%2C%20in%20an%20indictment%2C%20for%20allegedly%20orchestrating%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Gurpatwant%20Pannun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurpatwant-singh-pannun-assassination-plot-vikash-yadav-indian-panel-recommends-action-against-ex-spy-cc1-in-us-murder-plot-case-7479393%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Fireflies'%20Light%20Up%20Sky%20As%20India%20Gets%201st%20Private%20Satellite%20Constellation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Bengaluru-based%20space%20startup%20has%20made%20history%20by%20giving%20India%20the%20first%20private%20earth%20imaging%20satellite%20constellation.%20The%20constellation%20-'Firefly'%20-%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20Pixxel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPixxel%20-%20which%20has%20offices%20in%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20-%20was%20started%20in%202019%20by%20Awais%20Ahmed%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20while%20they%20were%20still%20studying%20at%20Birla%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Science%2C%20Pilani.%20They%20have%20already%20raised%20%2495%20million%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20India's%20satellite%20success%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvernight%2C%20three%20'Firefly'%20satellites%20were%20launched%20into%20550-kilometre%20low%20Earth%20orbit%2C%20using%20a%20SpaceX%20Falcon-9%20rocket%20from%20Vandenberg%20Space%20Force%20Base%2C%20California.%20Three%20more%20satellites%20will%20be%20launched%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongratulating%20Pixxel%20on%20this%20milestone%2C%20Dr%20Somanath%2C%20former%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20-%C2%A0under%20whose%20leadership%20new%20age%20space%20startups%20blossomed%20-%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20capability%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20a%20great%20boon%20to%20the%20sector%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20all%20precision%20earth%20imaging%20satellites%20from%20India%20have%20been%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20(ISRO)%20which%20has%20about%2052%20different%20satellites%20in%20space.%20Lately%2C%20India's%20burgeoning%20private%20space%20sector%20has%20been%20increasingly%20giving%20competition%20to%20the%20government%20behemoth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20data%20company%20said%20these%20satellites%20are%20designed%20to%20deliver%20critical%20climate%20and%20Earth%20insights%20with%20unmatched%20precision%2C%20each%20satellite%20sets%20a%20new%20benchmark%20in%20hyperspectral%20imaging.%20With%20advanced%20spectral%20capabilities%2C%20near%20real-time%20data%20collection%2C%20and%20wide-ranging%20applications%2C%20the%20'Firefly'%20constellation%20is%20poised%20to%20revolutionise%20how%20we%20understand%2C%20interact%20with%2C%20and%20safeguard%20our%20planet's%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Awais%20Ahmed%20(left)%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20founded%20Pixxel%20while%20still%20in%20college%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Awais%20Ahmed%20(left)%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20founded%20Pixxel%20while%20still%20in%20college%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fah02mr9o_pixxel-founders_625x300_15_January_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAwais%20Ahmed%20(left)%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20founded%20Pixxel%20while%20still%20in%20college.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20the%20singular%20achievement%20Lieutenant%20General%20Anil%20Bhat%20(retired)%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Association%20(IspA)%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPixxel%20has%20found%20a%20unique%20niche%20by%20giving%20the%20world%20high-end%20imaging%20satellites%20which%20are%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20both%20monitoring%20Earth%20and%20defence%20applications%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20today%20Pixxel%20is%20India's%20most%20well-funded%20space%20startup%20which%20took%20quick%20advantage%20of%20the%20opening%20up%20of%20the%20space%20sector%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Pixxel%20said%20the%20'Fireflies'%2C%20currently%20the%20world's%20highest-resolution%20commercial-grade%20hyperspectral%20satellites%2C%20bring%20unprecedented%20precision%20to%20monitoring%20the%20planet%20and%20setting%20a%20new%20benchmark%20for%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20capabilities.%20With%20a%20five-meter%20resolution%20attained%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20hyperspectral%20spacecraft%2C%20'Fireflies'%20are%20six%20times%20sharper%20than%20the%2030-meter%20standard%20of%20most%20existing%20hyperspectral%20satellites%2C%20capturing%20fine%20details%20previously%20invisible%20to%20conventional%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20our%20planet%20depends%20on%20how%20deeply%20we%20understand%20it%20today.%20The%20successful%20deployment%20of%20our%20first%20commercial%20satellites%20is%20a%20defining%20moment%20for%20Pixxel%20and%20a%20giant%20leap%20toward%20redefining%20how%20we%20use%20space%20technology%20to%20address%20the%20planet's%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Awais%20Ahmed%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Pixxel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPixxel's%20journey%20began%20in%20April%202022%20with%20the%20historic%20launch%20of%20'Shakuntala'%2C%20India's%20first%20private%20Earth-imaging%20hyperspectral%20satellite%2C%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20mission%20via%20Exolaunch%2C%20followed%20by%20'Anand'%20on%20ISRO's%20PSLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20milestones%20catalysed%20India's%20private%20space%20ecosystem%2C%20proving%20that%20Indian%20companies%20could%20deliver%20cutting-edge%20technology%20on%20par%20with%20global%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Fireflies'%20built%20on%20this%20legacy%2C%20embodying%20years%20of%20indigenous%20research%20and%20development%20and%20engineering%20excellence%20and%20a%20vision%20to%20bring%20globally%20relevant%20and%20meaningful%20Earth%20insights%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Firefly'%20constellation%20also%20marks%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20India's%20space%20journey%20as%20the%20nation's%20first%20commercial%20satellite%20constellation.%20These%20satellites%20surpass%20international%20standards%20in%20hyperspectral%20imaging%2C%20showcasing%20India's%20growing%20innovation%20and%20leadership%20in%20advanced%20space%20technology.%20They%20embody%20the%20spirit%20of%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAtmanirbharta%26quot%3B%20while%20highlighting%20the%20truly%20progressive%20impact%20of%20India's%20space%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKshitij%20Khandelwal%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20technology%20officer%20(CTO)%20of%20Pixxel%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20ability%20of%20'Firefly'%20to%20detect%20subtle%20changes%20in%20Earth's%20ecosystems%20will%20provide%20industries%20and%20governments%20with%20the%20precise%20information%20needed%20to%20address%20critical%20global%20challenges%20confidently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ahmed%20told%20Reuters%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20add%2018%20more%20spacecraft%20to%20the%20six%20it%20has%20already%20developed%2C%20eyeing%20a%20share%20of%20the%20satellite%20imaging%20market%20projected%20to%20reach%20%2419%20billion%20(roughly%20Rs%201%2C64%2C451%20crore)%20by%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736946360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fej2kqiao_firefly-statellite_625x300_15_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffireflies-light-up-sky-as-india-gets-1st-private-satellite-constellation-7480109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Bengaluru-based%20space%20startup%20has%20made%20history%20by%20giving%20India%20the%20first%20private%20earth%20imaging%20satellite%20constellation.%20The%20constellation%20-'Firefly'%20-%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20Pixxel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffireflies-light-up-sky-as-india-gets-1st-private-satellite-constellation-7480109%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Lodge%20FIR'%3A%20Poll%20official%20asks%20cops%20to%20probe%20BJP's%20