cal%20supporter%20of%20Trump's%20policies%20and%20has%20sought%20to%20strengthen%20ties%20between%20Italy%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20also%20received%20an%20invitation%20from%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20with%20spokesperson%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20highlighting%20the%20invitation%20as%20an%20example%20of%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20an%20open%20dialogue%20with%20leaders%20of%20countries%20that%20are%20not%20just%20our%20allies%20but%20our%20adversaries%20and%20our%20competitors%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20send%20a%20high-level%20envoy%20to%20represent%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHungarian%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%20has%20also%20received%20an%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%2C%20although%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20confirm%20his%20attendance.%20Orban%2C%20one%20of%20Trump's%20closest%20foreign%20allies%2C%20has%20been%20a%20key%20supporter%20of%20the%20president-elect's%20hard-right%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArgentine%20President%20Javier%20Milei%20will%20break%20tradition%20by%20attending%20the%20inauguration%20himself%2C%20rather%20than%20sending%20a%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Brazilian%20President%20Jair%20Bolsonaro%20also%20received%20an%20invitation%20for%20Trump's%20inauguration%20but%20is%20currently%20seeking%20to%20obtain%20a%20return%20of%20his%20confiscated%20passport%2C%20which%20was%20seized%20during%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%202023%20attempted%20coup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEl%20Salvador%20President%20Nayib%20Bukele%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20world%20leaders%20to%20congratulate%20Trump%20on%20his%20victory%20and%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration.%20Bukele%20has%20been%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20Trump's%20in%20Central%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Takeshi%20Iwaya%20will%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20as%20part%20of%20Japan's%20effort%20to%20bolster%20ties%20with%20the%20new%20administration.%20Iwaya%20has%20stated%20that%20Japan%20aims%20to%20build%20a%20relationship%20of%20trust%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20and%20his%20presence%20at%20the%20inauguration%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20gesture%20of%20goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20aim%20to%20build%20a%20relationship%20of%20trust%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Iwaya%20stated%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20NHK%2C%20Japan's%20public%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20will%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20inauguration%2C%20following%20an%20invitation%20from%20the%20Trump-Vance%20inaugural%20committee.%20Jaishankar's%20attendance%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20gesture%20of%20support%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20sought%20to%20strengthen%20ties%20with%20India%20and%20other%20key%20Asian%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20ministry%20statement%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Trump-Vance%20Inaugural%20Committee%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20will%20represent%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20at%20the%20Swearing-In%20Ceremony%20of%20President-Elect%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20notable%20attendees%20at%20the%20inauguration%20will%20include%20Eric%20Zemmour%2C%20a%20far-right%20politician%20from%20France%2C%20and%20Nigel%20Farage%2C%20a%20UK%20politician%20and%20long-time%20Trump%20ally.%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20with%20fellow%20billionaires%20-%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20will%20also%20be%20attended%20by%20former%20US%20Presidents%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20George%20W.%20Bush%2C%20and%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20who%20will%20be%20accompanied%20by%20their%20spouses%2C%20exce