%20on%20environmental%20pollution%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20in%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Mongolia.%20But%20after%20shooting%20the%20first%20segment%20in%20Delhi%2C%20she%20was%20moved%20to%20change%20perspectives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_375337209_6327442840715229_7021341370458285031_n_1080-1_11zon-1736739570-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Malaika%20Vaz%20Python%20Nat%20Geo%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_375337209_6327442840715229_7021341370458285031_n_1080-1_11zon-1736739570-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_375337209_6327442840715229_7021341370458285031_n_1080-1_11zon-1736739570-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_375337209_6327442840715229_7021341370458285031_n_1080-1_11zon-1736739570-150x187.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_375337209_6327442840715229_7021341370458285031_n_1080-1_11zon-1736739570.jpg%20766w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-397602%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMalaika%20Vaz%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20fascinating%20world%20of%20pythons.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20Indian%20woman%20now%20living%20in%20the%20West%2C%20telling%20a%20story%20about%20environmental%20pollution%20but%20only%20focusing%20on%20Asian%20countries%20is%20problematic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20issue%20of%20pollution%20didn%E2%80%99t%20belong%20solely%20to%20the%20developing%20world.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20often%20there%20are%20large%