%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsome-dues-left-mallikarjun-kharges-sharp-jibe-at-lt-chairman-over-90-hour-work-week-remark%2Farticleshow%2F117266951.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%20on%20bed%20rest%2C%20will%20not%20be%20rushed%20back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736939736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117266611%2Cimgsize-31224.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fjasprit-bumrah-on-bed-rest-will-not-be-rushed-back%2Farticleshow%2F117266492.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20advised%20bed%20rest%20at%20home%20due%20to%20swelling%20in%20his%20back%20following%20a%20long%20tour%20of%20Australia.%20The%20exact%20diagnosis%20and%20future%20course%20of%20action%20will%20be%20determined%20once%20the%20swelling%20subsides.%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20cricket%20will%20be%20carefully%20managed%20to%20avoid%20aggravating%20his%20back%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAHIL%20MALHOTRA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fjasprit-bumrah-on-bed-rest-will-not-be-rushed-back%2Farticleshow%2F117266492.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20'I%20Sleep%20With%20One%20Eye%20Open'%3A%20LA%20Residents%20On%20Life%20In%20A%20City%20On%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20strange%20feeling%20when%20I%20walked%20past%20the%20homes%20taken%20by%20the%20fires%20at%20Pasadena%20and%20Altadena%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20A%20feeling%20like%20I%20had%20been%20there%20before.%20But%20I%20knew%20I%20hadn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20did%20the%20brick%20chimney%20columns%20and%20arches%20leading%20to%20nowhere%20remind%20me%20of%3F%20Ruins.%20That%20is%20what%20it%20was.%20Ruins%20that%20I'd%20seen%20on%20my%20travels%20or%20in%20postcards.%20What%20was%20once%20an%20era%20is%20now%20a%20fading%20silhouette.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20residential%20areas%20of%20Pasadena%20and%20Altadena%2C%20where%20I%20walked%20alone%2C%20on%20the%20deserted%20streets%2C%20the%20fires%20had%20consigned%20what%20were%20people's%20homes%2C%20as%20of%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20to%20the%20forever%20past.%20Their%20little%20civilisation%2C%20which%20was%20their%20world%2C%20was%20done.%20Such%20was%20the%20cruel%20arbitrariness%20of%20the%20raging%20fires%20that%20a%20random%20home%20next%20door%20or%20next%20block%20could%20still%20be%20standing%20intact%20while%20others%20return%20to%20a%20charred%20nothingness%2C%20arches%20and%20chimney%20pillars%2C%20a%20fireplace%2C%20the%20shell%20of%20a%20car.%20There's%20no%20saying%20what%20survives.%20Entire%20rooms%20vanished%2C%20books%2C%20furniture%2C%20kitchen%20cabinets%2C%20dishes%2C%20clothing%2C%20sofas%2C%20tables%2C%20curtains%2C%20walls%2C%20roofs%2C%20will%20all%20be%20gone%20without%20a%20trace.%20Maybe%2C%20a%20bathtub%20would%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20Our%20Entire%20Community'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20rebuilding%20lives%20lost%20to%20a%20fire%20can%20take%20years.%20With%20fire%20insurance%20becoming%20scarce%20or%20prohibitive%20over%20the%20years%2C%20many%20don't%20have%20the%20financial%20cover.%20Those%20who%20can%20may%20want%20to%20rebuild%20in%20the%20same%20neighbourhood%20community%20they%20have%20lived%20in%20for%20years.%20Yet%2C%20for%20some%20like%20Kristin%20from%20the%20Palisades%2C%20there%20is%20no%20neighbourhood%20left%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKristin%2C%20who%20spent%20the%20last%2015%20years%20raising%20her%20children%20in%20the%20Palisades%2C%20came%20home%20from%20vacation%20to%20learn%20that%20her%20home%20was%20gone%2C%20and%20so%20was%20the%20brick-and-mortar%20existence%20of%20her%20entire%20community.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20all%20my%20family%20albums%2C%20the%20sentimental%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20clutching%20her%20chest.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20the%20watch%20my%20father%20gave%20me.%20I%20only%20have%20the%20stuff%20I%20took%20with%20me%20in%20my%20suitcase%20for%20a%20holiday.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20just%20us.%20It%20is%20our%20entire%20community.%20Though%20I%20am%20thankful%20my%20family%20is%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20showing%20me%20pictures%20of%20levelled%20land%20that%20was%20once%20the%20community%20church%2C%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20heartbroken%20for%20my%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFire%20and%20tragedy%20bring%20people%20closer%20together.%20It%20makes%20people%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20when%20they%20might%20not%20have%20earlier.%20It%20makes%20them%20see%20each%20other%20for%20who%20they%20are%20and%2C%20to%20a%20degree%2C%20trust%20each%20other%20more.%20Earlier%20that%20morning%2C%20with%20so%20many%20road%20closures%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20go%20about%20reaching%20the%20sites%20of%20the%20fires%20from%20my%20downtown%20hotel.%20The%20hotel%20doorman%20suggested%20a%20route%20to%20my%20Armenian%20American%20taxi%20driver%2C%20who%20then%20called%20his%20friend%20in%20Pasadena%20to%20see%20exactly%20which%20roads%20to%20take.%20A%20police%20officer%20on%20duty%20believed%20me%20when%20I%20said%20I%20had%20a%20story%20to%20report%20and%20asked%20another%20reporter%20with%20a%20personal%20car%20to%20give%20me%20a%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20With%20Uncertainty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reporter%2C%20who%20didn't%20know%20me%20at%20all%2C%20willingly%20drove%20me%20and%20then%20offered%20me%20a%20mask.%20Delhi's%20winter%20air%20was%20not%20a%20patch%20on%20these%20toxic%20fumes.%20At%20times%20like%20these%2C%20even%20strangers%20come%20together%20to%20help%20each%20other.%20It%20will%20take%20that%20spirit%20of%20community%2C%20if%20not%20its%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20get%20through%20this%20travail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20walk%20past%20bright%20white%20rose%20bushes%20blooming%20on%20a%20gleaming%20white%20picket%20fence%2C%20still%20guarding%20a%20house%20that%20is%20entirely%20burnt%20down.%20A%20surreal%20sight.%20But%20the%20devastation%20leads%20me%20to%20wonder%20about%20the%20emotional%20toll%20this%20disaster%20has%20taken%20not%20just%20on%20those%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20homes%2C%20but%20also%20on%20those%20who%20are%20living%20with%20uncertainty%2C%20knowing%20that%20with%20more%20winds%20expected%20this%20week%2C%20it%20might%20be%20their%20time%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20sleep%20with%20one%20eye%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lee%20Roy%20Lahey%2C%20an%20artist%20in%20LA's%20famous%20animation%20industry.%20Lee%20Roy%20says%20that%20many%20middle-class%20workers%20in%20animation%20have%20been%20badly%20affected%20by%20the%20Eaton%20fire%20that%20razed%20Altadena%20and%20Pasadena.%20While%20celebrity%20homes%20make%20news%2C%20many%20others%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20have%20been%20also%20hit%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20a%20state%20of%20constant%20vigilance%20and%20intelligence%20gathering%2C%20trying%20to%20preserve%20some%20semblance%20of%20normalcy%20for%20their%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20catastrophising%20in%20front%20of%20the%20kids.%20Yet%2C%20if%20we%20wait%20too%20long%20and%20something%20happens%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20will%20be%20a%20really%20big%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20daily%20negotiations%20that%20young%20families%20who%20have%20not%20had%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%2C%20face.%20But%20there%20is%20hope.%20A%20community%20GoFundMe%20page%20has%20friends%20from%20the%20animation%20industry%20supporting%20each%20other.%20Storyboard%20artists%2C%20VFX%20engineers%2C%20illustrators%2C%20whose%20names%20are%20on%20the%20credits%20of%20some%20of%20my%20children's%20favourite%20cartoons%2C%20have%20lost%20their%20homes%20entirely%20and%20have%20nothing%20left%20to%20rebuild.%20Yet%2C%20each%20family%20appears%20to%20have%20gathered%20some%20funds%20to%20help%20them%20restart%20their%20lives.%20And%20they%20are%20full%20of%20humility%20and%20gratitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20gratitude%20a%20survival%20mechanism%3F%20The%20cynic%20in%20me%20sometimes%20wonders.%20Or%20is%20it%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20an%20instant%20levelling-up%20of%20one's%20humanity%20brought%20forth%20by%20life's%20great%20teacher%3A%20loss%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amrita%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20television%20host%2C%20writer%20and%20producer)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736939580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1d19rdag_la-wildfire_625x300_08_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fi-sleep-with-one-eye-open-la-residents-on-life-in-a-city-on-fire-7479442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20residential%20areas%20of%20Pasadena%20and%20Altadena%2C%20where%20I%20walked%20alone%2C%20on%20the%20deserted%20streets%2C%20the%20fires%20had%20consigned%20what%20were%20people's%20homes%2C%20as%20of%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20to%20the%20forever%20past.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fi-sleep-with-one-eye-open-la-residents-on-life-in-a-city-on-fire-7479442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20BCCI%20Scrutiny%2C%20'Strict'%20Gambhir%20Had%20Rift%20With%20Support%20Staff%20During%20BGT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E's%20stint%20a