0Trade%20Centre%20attacks%20in%20New%20York%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-airlines-pakistan-pm-orders-probe-after-airlines-ad-evokes-9-11-memories-7478541%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20blasts%20US%20forced%20labour%20claims%20as%20'groundless'%20after%20import%20ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736931896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117262189%2Cimgsize-1058150.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-blasts-us-forced-labour-claims-as-groundless-after-import-ban%2Farticleshow%2F117262162.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117262162.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina%20condemned%20US%20import%20bans%20on%2037%20additional%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20calling%20the%20forced%20labour%20allegations%20'malicious'%20and%20'groundless.'%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security's%20move%20targets%20firms%20involved%20in%20mining%20and%20processing%20minerals%2C%20textile%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20solar%20module%20production%20in%20Xinjiang%2C%20where%20Beijing%20is%20accused%20of%20detaining%20Uyghurs.%20China%20vows%20to%20protect%20its%20firms'%20rights%20and%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-blasts-us-forced-labour-claims-as-groundless-after-import-ban%2Farticleshow%2F117262162.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-blasts-us-forced-labour-claims-as-groundless-after-import-ban%2Famp_articleshow%2F117262162.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-blasts-us-forced-labour-claims-as-groundless-after-import-ban%2Famp_articleshow%2F117262162.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Ban%20To%20Buyout%3A%20What%20Next%20For%20TikTok%20In%20The%20US%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETikTok%20faces%20an%20imminent%20shutdown%20in%20the%20United%20States%20after%20Congress%20passed%20a%20law%20last%20year%20forcing%20its%20Chinese%20owner%20ByteDance%20to%20either%20sell%20the%20platform%20or%20close%20it%20by%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20expected%20to%20rule%20this%20week%20on%20TikTok's%20challenge%20to%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20hearing%20last%20Friday%2C%20expectations%20are%20high%20that%20the%20law%20will%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20review%20of%20what%20could%20happen%20next%20for%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApp%20Store%20Ban%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20ban%2C%20the%20US%20government%20would%20first%20direct%20Apple%20and%20Google%20to%20remove%20TikTok%20from%20their%20app%20stores%2C%20preventing%20new%20downloads%20as%20early%20as%20Sunday%2C%20a%20day%20before%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20takes%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20app%20would%20remain%20on%20the%20phones%20of%20the%20existing%20170%20million%20US%20users%20unless%20TikTok%20directly%20blocks%20their%20access.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20TikTok%20lawyer%20Noel%20Francisco%20stated%20the%20site%20would%20%26quot%3Bgo%20dark%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%20if%20the%20justices%20fail%20to%20block%20the%20ban%2C%20many%20observers%20doubt%20ByteDance%20would%20unilaterally%20hit%20the%20off%20switch%20for%20American%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20indicated%20as%20much%20in%20a%20memo%20to%20staff%2C%20cited%20in%20the%20Verge%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20offices%20will%20remain%20open%26quot%3B%20regardless%20of%20what%20happens%20on%20January%2019th%20and%20employees%20will%20keep%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20is%20not%20written%20in%20a%20way%20that%20impacts%20the%20entities%20through%20which%20you%20are%20employed%2C%20only%20the%20US%20user%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorkarounds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20TikTok%20keeps%20its%20app%20accessible%2C%20US%20users%20would%20stop%20receiving%20security%20and%20software%20updates%2C%20leading%20to%20gradual%20deterioration%20in%20quality%20and%20increased%20vulnerabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20workaround%2C%20users%20might%20turn%20to%20VPNs%20(virtual%20private%20networks)%20to%20mask%20their%20location%20by%20routing%20through%20countries%20where%20TikTok%20remains%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20TikTok%20could%20update%20from%20non-US%20servers%20through%20partnerships%20with%20foreign%2C%20non-Chinese%20companies%20--%20though%20this%20would%20constitute%20direct%20defiance%20of%20US%20authorities%20and%20likely%20intensify%20scrutiny%20of%20ByteDance's%20US%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefiance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Trump%20takes%20office%2C%20the%20law's%20implementation%20will%20fall%20to%20his%20attorney%20general%2C%20who%20could%20choose%20not%20to%20enforce%20it%2C%20or%20stall%2C%20defying%20Congress's%20overwhelming%20support%20for%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20might%20also%20approach%20the%20Republican%20majority%20in%20Congress%20to%20modify%20the%20law%2C%20potentially%20giving%20ByteDance%20more%20time%20to%20find%20a%20buyer%20or%20devise%20alternative%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlternatives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20banned%2C%20the%20assumption%20is%20that%20TikTok%20users%20will%20move%20to%20other%20apps%2C%20like%20Instagram%20Reels%20and%20YouTube%20shorts%2C%20TikTok%20copycats%20that%20have%20grown%20and%20will%20directly%20benefit%20from%20their%20rival's%20demise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20X%20could%20also%20benefit%20and%20the%20tycoon%20has%20made%20it%20known%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20platform%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20to%20more%20closely%20resemble%20TikTok%2C%20with%20video%20content%20and%20shopping%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20expressed%20concern%20that%20a%20ban%20would%20primarily%20advantage%20Meta-owned%20Instagram%2C%20which%20may%20explain%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20recent%20public%20support%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20American%20content%20creators%20have%20already%20migrated%20to%20Xiaohongshu%20(Red%20Note)%2C%20another%20Chinese%20social%20media%20app%20that%20recently%20topped%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20downloads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestor%20Rescue%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20potential%20buyers%20have%20emerged%2C%20including%20a%20group%20led%20by%20Frank%20McCourt%2C%20former%20owner%20of%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodgers%2C%20even%20if%20ByteDance%20has%20ruled%20out%20a%20sale%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20partner%20in%20the%20bid%2C%20Canadian%20businessman%20Kevin%20O'Leary%2C%20recently%20golfed%20with%20Trump%20and%20reported%20the%20president-elect's%20desire%20to%20use%20the%20TikTok%20saga%20as%20leverage%20in%20US-China%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20that%20the%20Chinese%20authorities%20would%20be%20open%20to%20a%20buyout%20by%20Musk%20was%20denied%20by%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Activision%20Blizzard%20CEO%20Bobby%20Kotick%20also%20remains%20interested%20in%20buying%20TikTok%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20TikTok's%20fate%20rests%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20with%20the%20company%20lawyers%20asking%20the%20nine%20justices%20for%20a%20delay%20to%20any%20ban%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3Bbreat