ce%20in%201947%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20every%20single%20Indian%20and%20it's%20about%20time%20we%20stop%20listening%20to%20this%20nonsense%20that%20these%20people%20think%20they%20can%20just%20keep%20parroting%20out%20and%20shouting%20and%20screaming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhagwat%20was%20in%20Indore%20on%20Monday%20to%20present%20the%20National%20Devi%20Ahilya%20award%20to%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust.%20Addressing%20a%20gathering%20there%2C%20he%20said%20the%20day%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20should%20be%20celebrated%20as%20%26quot%3BPratishtha%20Dwadashi%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20marks%20the%20%26quot%3Btrue%20independence%26quot%3B%20of%20Bharat.%20%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20which%20faced%20enemy%20attacks%20for%20centuries%2C%20witnessed%20its%20true%20independence%20that%20day.%20We%20had%20independence%2C%20but%20it%20had%20not%20been%20established.%20India%20got%20political%20independence%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20we%20also%20brought%20a%20Constitution%20but%20the%20country%20did%20not%20run%20in%20its%20spirit.%20How%20can%20we%20accept%20that%20dreams%20have%20been%20fulfilled%20and%20pain%20alleviated%3F%20Our%20swa%20(self)%20is%20Ram%2C%20Krishna%20and%20Shiva.%20Do%20they%20belong%20only%20to%20those%20who%20worship%20them%3F%20No.%20Ram%20connects%20people%20from%20north%20to%20south%2C%20Krishna%20from%20east%20to%20west%20and%20Shiva%20is%20in%20every%20particle%20of%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20the%20Opposition%20was%20fighting%20not%20just%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20State.%20%26quot%3BOur%20ideology%20like%20the%20RSS%20ideology%20is%20thousands%20of%20years%20old%20and%20it%20has%20been%20fighting%20the%20RSS%20ideology%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20Do%20not%20think%20that%20we%20are%20fighting%20