es%20to%20carry%20out%20separate%20tests%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn8x5gm4k1xo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn8x5gm4k1xo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn8x5gm4k1xo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Delhi%20Elections%3A%20BJP%20Still%20Hasn't%20Found%20An%20Answer%20To%20Kejriwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20Delhi%20assembly%20election%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20political%20battles%20in%20recent%20times.%20It's%20a%20contest%20between%20two%20titans%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20hate%20to%20lose.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20would%20not%20like%20to%20be%20trounced%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row.%20And%20Kejriwal%20knows%20that%20if%20Modi%20vanquishes%20him%20in%20his%20own%20fortress%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20of%20his%20political%20career.%20For%20both%20leaders%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20too%20high.%20No%20other%20politician%20has%20defeated%20Modi%20as%20overwhelmingly%20as%20Kejriwal%20has%20in%20successive%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20national%20capital%20remains%20out%20of%20the%20BJP's%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20started%20his%20political%20career%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20was%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20he%20first%20experimented%20with%20electoral%20politics%20and%20mesmerised%20the%20nation%20with%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20politics.%20Even%20before%20Modi's%20rise%20on%20the%20national%20stage%2C%20Kejriwal%20was%20the%20darling%20of%20the%20media%20and%20the%20middle%20class.%20It%20was%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20miracle%20that%20a%20ragtag%20army%20of%20novices%20led%20by%20Kejriwal%20defeated%20Modi%2C%20despite%20the%20BJP's%20formidable%20election%20machinery%2C%20in%20the%202015%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20defeat%20was%20historic.%20The%20BJP%20could%20win%20only%20three%20of%20the%2070%20seats.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20Modi%20tried%20to%20seek%20revenge%2C%20he%20lost%20again.%20Kejriwal%20rejoiced%20in%20his%20hubris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Transformation%20Of%20The%20'Aam%20Aadmi'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202020%2C%20however%2C%20Kejriwal%20was%20no%20longer%20the%20same%20man.%20The%20radical%20revolutionary%20had%20transformed%20himself%20into%20a%20Machiavellian%20politician%20with%20no%20ideological%20commitment.%20Retaining%20the%20chief%20minister's%20office%20became%20his%20sole%20objective.%20After%20the%20victory%20in%20Punjab%20and%20partial%20success%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20AAP%20became%20a%20national%20party%2C%20joining%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20major%20political%20forces%20currently.%20Among%20regional%20parties%2C%20the%20AAP%20is%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20governments%20in%20two%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%202025%20Delhi%20election%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20toughest%20battle%20for%20the%20AAP.%20The%20party%20is%20grappling%20with%20over%2010%20years%20of%20incumbency%2C%20along%20with%20serious%20corruption%20charges%20against%20its%20leaders%2C%20including%20Kejriwal.%20He%20knows%20better%20than%20anyone%20that%20a%20loss%20in%20Delhi%20is%20unacceptable.%20Such%20a%20defeat%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20confirmation%20that%20the%20corruption%20charges%20levelled%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20led%20to%20jail%20terms%20for%20senior%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Kejriwal%2C%20hold%20some%20weight.%20It%20would%20also%20signal%20that%20his%20promise%20to%20create%20a%20corruption-free%20society%20was%20a%20farce%20and%20an%20opportunistic%20tool%20to%20win%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKejriwal%20On%20The%20Move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20after%20securing%20bail%20and%20being%20released%20from%20Tihar%2C%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20constantly%20on%20the%20move.%20His%20first%20two%20steps%20indicate%20his%20nervousness.%20He%20resigned%20as%20chief%20minister%20and%20appointed%20Atishi%20in%20his%20place.%20Then%2C%20he%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20chief%20minister's%20bungalow%2C%20which%20had%20become%20controversial.%20This%20was%20his%20attempt%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20corruption%20charges%20and%20present%20himself%20as%20a%20victim%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20public.%20He%20had%20previously%20stated%20that%20he%20would%20return%20to%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%20only%20after%20being%20cleared%20in%20the%20people's%20court.%20He%20has%20since%20focused%20on%20a%20mass%20contact%20programme%2C%20visiting%20people%20daily%20and%20conducting%20door-to-door%20campaigns.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20is%20engaging%20directly%20with%20voters%20and%20sending%20the%20message%20that%20he%20has%20been%20victimised%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20and%20that%20the%20corruption%20charges%20against%20him%20are%20baseless%20and%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20conspiracy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiberal%20Dose%20Of%20Freebies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20has%20since%20been%20making%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20promises.%20He%20has%20rolled%20out%20an%20attractive%20basket%20of%20freebies%2C%20including%20Rs%202%2C100%20for%20women%20voters%20and%20free%20medical%20treatment%20for%20senior%20citizens%20aged%2060%20and%20above.%20To%20counter%20the%20BJP's%20Hindutva%20narrative%2C%20he%20has%20promised%20that%20if%20he%20wins%2C%20his%20government%20will%20provide%20Rs%2018%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20salary%20to%20Hindu%20priests%20and%20Sikh%20granthis.%20To%20win%20the%20support%20of%20urban%20colonies%2C%20he%20has%20announced%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20that%20his%20government%20would%20provide%20funds%20to%20Resident%20Welfare%20Associations%20(RWAs)%20to%20hire%20private%20guards%20if%20his%20party%20returns%20to%20power%20in%20the%20February%205%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20has%2C%20of%20course%2C%20built%20a%20strong%20record%20of%20promising%20and%20delivering%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20AAP's%20remarkable%20victories%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20election.%20Like%20Modi's%20Gujarat%20model%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20been%20promoting%20the%20Delhi%20model%20of%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20But%20Kejriwal%20knows%20that%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20in%20politics%2C%20and%20old%20promises%20have%20limited%20staying%20power.%20To%20attract%20new%20voters%20while%20maintaining%20his%20existing%20social%20base%2C%20new%20promises%20are%20necessary.%20The%20latest%20promises%20of%20freebies%20should%20be%20understood%20in%20that%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Bipolar%20Contest%20Is%20Inevitable%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20for%20some%20strange%20reason%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20not%20have%20learned%20from%20its%20past%20mistakes.%20Since%201998%2C%20the%20party%20has%20remained%20out%20of%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%20despite%20having%20won%20all%20seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20three%20general%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20has%20a%20strong%20social%20base%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20consistently%20securing%2032%25%20to%2039%25%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20assembly%20elections.%20Even%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20MCD%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20secure%2039%25%20votes.%20The%20party's%20biggest%20failure%20in%20assembly%20elections%20has%20been%20its%20inability%20to%20raise%20its%20vote%20share%20beyond%2040%25%2C%20which%20is%20necessary%20to%20win%20and%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Delhi.%20In%201993%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20first%20formed%20a%20government%2C%20it%20secured%2047.82%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20had%2047.76%25.%20In%20the%201998%2C%202003%2C%20and%202008%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%2047.76%25%2C%2048.13%25%20and%2040.31%25%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20In%201993%2C%20the%20BJP%20benefited%20from%20Madan%20Lal%20Khurana's%20strong%20leadership%2C%20while%20Sheila%20Dikshit%20later%20led%20the%20Congress%20to%20form%20successive%20governments.%20Since%20the%20deaths%20of%20Madan%20Lal%20Khurana%20and%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20failed%20to%20produce%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20same%20stature%20or%20charisma%20as%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20make%20this%20election%20triangular.%20But%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections%20has%20not%20been%20inspiring.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20party%20had%20only%204.26%25%20votes%2C%20though%20in%20parliament%20elections%2C%20its%20showing%20has%20been%20better.%20Can%20the%20Congress%20surprise%20Delhi%20voters%20and%20political%20pundits%3F%20Even%20a%20hyper-optimistic%20watcher%20may%20not%20bet%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20elections%20are%20once%20again%20likely%20to%20be%20bipolar.%20The%20Congress%20may%20manage%20to%20secure%20a%20few%20seats%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20major%20player.%20While%20it's%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20AAP's%20vote%20share%20could%20shrink%2C%20the%20million-dollar%20question%20is%20whether%20it%20will%20decrease%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%2040%25%20threshold.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20the%20AAP%20will%20be%20in%20serious%20trouble.%20But%2C%20for%20this%20to%20occur%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20decode%20the%20%E2%80%98K'%20Factor.%20Can%20it%20do%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736928060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2dqsql6g_kejriwal_625x300_15_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-elections-bjp-still-hasnt-found-an-answer-to-kejriwal-7478022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22hile%20its%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20AAP's%20vote%20share%20could%20shrink%2C%20the%20million-dollar%20question%20is%20whether%20it%20will%20decrease%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%2040%25%20threshold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-elections-bjp-still-hasnt-found-an-answer-to-kejriwal-7478022%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20as%20SpaceX%20rocket%20blasts%20off%20to%20the%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736927296000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8470%2Flive%2Fc192e150-d314-11ef-9fd6-0be88a764111.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc74mxxz2v8vo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20took%20off%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20carrying%20two%20lunar%20landers%20and%20a%20micro%20rover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc74mxxz2v8vo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20notice%20to%20Centre%20on%20Cong%20plea%20challenging%20changed%20poll%20rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736926912000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117259249%2Cimgsize-2067238.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-issues-notice-to-centre-on-congress-plea-challenging-changed-election-rules%2Farticleshow%2F1