p%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%2017-YO%20Is%20Empowering%20Marginalised%20Students%2C%20Tackling%20Textile%20Waste%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Creating%20Jobs%20for%20the%20Underprivileged%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bustling%20city%20of%20Nagpur%2C%2017-year-old%20Tejas%20Pugalia%2C%20a%20class%2012%20student%20at%20Centre%20Point%20School%2C%20is%20driven%20by%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20help%20others.%20What%20started%20as%20tutoring%20a%20friend%20from%20a%20marginalised%20community%20soon%20uncovered%20a%20much%20larger%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20in%202022%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20help%20the%20son%20of%20a%20household%20maid%20with%20his%20studies.%20The%20boy%2C%20younger%20than%20Tejas%2C%20lived%20in%20a%20world%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20tutored%20him%2C%20I%20learnt%20about%20the%20struggles%20children%20face%20in%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20alarming%20issues%20I%20learnt%20was%20that%20many%20children%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20school%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20bags%20and%20their%20books%20would%20get%20ruined.%20Instead%2C%20some%20had%20to%20take%20up%20household%20chores%20or%20get%20involved%20in%20child%20labour%2C%20creating%20a%20gap%20in%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20was%20deeply%20moved%20as%20he%20realised%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20school%20bag%20was%20preventing%20children%20in%20government%20schools%20from%20continuing%20their%20education%20during%20monsoons.%20It%20was%20a%20problem%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20solve%20sustainably.%20With%20his%20curiosity%20piqued%20and%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20helping%2C%20he%20thought%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20upcycling%20textile%20waste%2C%20a%20serious%20environmental%20issue%2C%20and%20using%20it%20to%20create%20school%20bags%20that%20would%20be%20eco-friendly%20and%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Threads4Good%20came%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20moment%20that%20stirred%20the%20idea%20for%20%E2%80%98Threads4Good%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20on%20empathy%20and%20the%20belief%20that%20communities%20can%20unite%20to%20solve%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20pressing%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20task%20he%20could%20tackle%20alone%20and%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20collaboration.%20%E2%80%9CI%20needed%20help%2C%20but%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20to%20start.%20I%20turned%20to%20my%20connections%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%2C%20I%20had%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20volunteers%20from%20all%20over%20India%2C%20eager%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-18-at-1.14.21-PM-1_11zon-1736083535.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tejas%20and%20his%20team%20conduct%20regular%20quality%20checks%20to%20ensure%20the%20bags%20are%20durable%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22